<h2><a class="listing" style="link" href="/en/Dossiers/CTA-and-S-T/Selected-publications/International-Assessment-of-Agricultural-Science-and-Technology-for-Development" title="International Assessment of Agricultural Science and Technology for Development" alt="link">International Assessment of Agricultural Science and Technology for Development</a></h2>

	
					<p><i>Final report of the Steering Committee, World Bank Group, August 2003</i> </p>
							<p><span class="date">22/12/2004</span></p>
	<div class="cnt">
	<a class="link" href="/en/Dossiers/CTA-and-S-T/Selected-publications/International-Assessment-of-Agricultural-Science-and-Technology-for-Development">Read more...</a>
