<h2><a class="listing" style="link" href="/en/Dossiers/CTA-and-S-T/Selected-publications/Emerging-Issues-in-S-T-for-Food-Security-and-Sustainable-Development-in-Africa" title="Emerging Issues in S&amp;T for Food Security and Sustainable Development in Africa" alt="link">Emerging Issues in S&amp;T for Food Security and Sustainable Development in Africa</a></h2>

	
					<p><i>Ed. L.J. Unnevehr, IFPRI, Sept. 2003</i>. 17 policy briefs describing 'how developing countries are addressing food safety issues in order to improve both food security and food trade, and discusses the risks, benefits, and costs when such policies are implemented'.</p>
							<p><span class="date">22/12/2004</span></p>
	<div class="cnt">
	<a class="link" href="/en/Dossiers/CTA-and-S-T/Selected-publications/Emerging-Issues-in-S-T-for-Food-Security-and-Sustainable-Development-in-Africa">Read more...</a>
